#!/usr/local/projects/routing/help/html_filter.pl
<h2 align=center>Help for the "Distributor" field of the "Patron" table</h2>
The Distributor field will always remain the same for a patron, containing the
name of the base of operations that provides them with these services.  Patrons may
get shifted from route to route, from driver to driver, but they will always remain
under the same distributor.

